data.description: Recent price improvement! Welcome home to this Central Tucson Ranch style charmer! The beautiful custom wrought iron door welcomes you into the living room and kitchen area that is perfect for entertaining! Spacious floor plan with 4 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms. The primary bedroom & en-suite bathroom  has 2 closets & private access to the backyard. The covered back porch provides a cozy retreat. NO HOA! The large lot size of 0.15 acres has plenty of space for all of your toys. There is a carport to shade your vehicle & a workshop for all of your weekend projects. Great curb appeal with low care desert landscaping. The convenient Central location is close to all of the places you love! There is a municipal park within just a few blocks, along with restaurants, shopping, services, & more nearby
